Create KPI Visualization 13

   CREATE KPI VISUALIZATION

DAYS TO CLOSE

  1. Click on KPI Visualization
  2. INDICATOR FIELD:    Drag and drop .MTD_TimetocloseDay(DAX Measures Tables)  
  3. TREND AXIS FIELD:     Drag and drop Month(Date Table)
  4. TARGET GOALS FIELDS:     Drag and drop .PrevM_TimetocloseDay


1st Rsp Time

  1. Click on KPI Visualization
  2. INDICATOR FIELD:    Drag and drop .MTD1stResTime(DAX Measures Tables)  
  3. TREND AXIS FIELD:     Drag and drop Day(Date Table)
  4. TARGET GOALS FIELDS:     Drag and drop firstResTimeGoal(Goal Table)

1st Contact Res

  1. Click on KPI Visualization
  2. INDICATOR FIELD:    Drag and drop .MTD_FirstContactRate(DAX Measures Tables)  
  3. TREND AXIS FIELD:     Drag and drop Month(Date Table)
  4. TARGET GOALS FIELDS:     Drag and drop FirstContactResolutionRate(Goal Table)

RESOLVED

  1. Click on KPI Visualization
  2. INDICATOR FIELD:    Drag and drop CurM_resolved%(DAX Measures Tables)  
  3. TREND AXIS FIELD:     Drag and drop Month(Date Table)
  4. TARGET GOALS FIELDS:     Drag and SolvedTicketGoals(Goal Table)
